trends: There have been 15 other sightings in Moose Jaw

divs: Sighting DetailsVery bright star-like object went over Moose Jaw around 11:30 PM on June 13, 2011, followed later by two dim star-like objects side-by-side. There may have been indication of a (not-so) stealth aircraft as there was one brief 'flash' of light too quick to determine whether it was stationary or not. ..
